data.text:
Over 2,000 Frames Available In-Store

In a hurry? Don't worry. Eyemart's advanced on site labs can create most custom prescriptions in about an hour.

Located conveniently inside Eyemart Express in Eugene, OR, Dr. Ben E. Coutant's practice offers an unparalleled eyewear shopping experience. Eyemart Express boasts a vast selection of over 2,000 frames, catering to every style and budget. From the high-fashion designs of Fendi and Armani to the sporty styles of Nike and the classic elegance of Calvin Klein, there is something for everyone. The frames are thoughtfully categorized by gender and price, making your shopping experience straightforward and enjoyable.

In addition to a wide range of designer options, Eyemart Express is renowned for its cutting-edge on-site labs that can deliver custom prescription glasses in about an hourâ€”perfect for those in a rush. The convenience doesn't stop there; Eyemart Express also offers a unique Home Try-on service. This service allows you to select frames from the comfort of your home, ensuring you find the perfect fit and style without having to leave your house. Whether you need new glasses immediately or prefer to take your time choosing the right pair, Eyemart Express in Eugene provides the flexibility and quality you deserve.
